==English==

===Pronunciation===
*kīt, /kaɪt/, /<tt>kaIt</tt>/
*:[[Rhymes:English:-aɪt|Rhymes: -aɪt]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# A [[bird of prey]] with long wings and weak legs that mostly feeds on [[carrion]] and spends long periods [[soar]]ing.
# A heavier than air object which [[fly|flies]] in the air by obtaining [[lift]] from wind, and is tethered by a [[line]] or a [[string]].
# {{cattag|geometry}} A [[quadrilateral]] having two pairs of edges of equal length, the edges of each pair being consecutive.
# {{cattag|slang}} An [[aircraft]], or [[aeroplane]].

